title: What So Not
description:
A duo consisting of upcoming star Flume and powerhouse Emoh Instead is the definition of What So Not. I've put most of their releases into a torrent since it's pretty difficult to find any of this stuff for free elsewhere. Some of the stuff here is ripped from Soundcloud. I apologize for that but, like I said, it's really difficult to find any of this stuff for free elsewhere. Regardless, enjoy the music. The rips don't sound too bad at all.
